{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Blob.arrayBuffer()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob/arrayBuffer","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_API\">File API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>构造函数</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob/Blob\"><code>Blob()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob/size\"><code>size</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob/type\"><code>type</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><em><code>arrayBuffer()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob/slice\"><code>slice()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob/stream\"><code>stream()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob/text\"><code>text()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>File API 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileList\"><code>FileList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReaderSync\"><code>FileReaderSync</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURL\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>URL.revokeObjectURL()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>arrayBuffer()</code></strong> 方法返回一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> 对象，包含 blob 中的数据，并在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a> 中以二进制数据的形式呈现。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">var bufferPromise = blob.arrayBuffer();\n\nblob.arrayBuffer().then(buffer =&gt; /* 处理 ArrayBuffer 数据的代码……*/);\n\nvar buffer = await blob.arrayBuffer();\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<p>无须提供任何参数。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>返回一个 promise 对象，在 resolved 状态中以二进制的形式包含 blob 中的数据，并呈现在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a> 中。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"异常","title":"异常","isH3":true,"content":"<p>当执行这个方法没有提示错误时，那么它可能会出现在 promise 的 reject 状态中。这是可能发生的，比如说在用于获取 blob 数据的一段代码抛出异常的时候。在读取数据时抛出的任何异常都会被放入 reject 状态中。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用须知","title":"使用须知","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsArrayBuffer\"><code>FileReader.readAsArrayBuffer()</code></a> 这个方法与之类似，但 <code>arrayBuffer()</code> 返回一个 promise 对象，而不是像 <code>FileReader</code> 一样返回一个基于事件的 API。</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/FileAPI/#dom-blob-arraybuffer","title":"File API"}],"query":"api.Blob.arrayBuffer"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Blob.arrayBuffer","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob/arrayBuffer/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另见","title":"另见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Response/arrayBuffer\"><code>Body.arrayBuffer()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a